      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think the Jewish phenomenon is to-- to burden your children with education rather than anything else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think I've got that from my experience in Germany.",
